{"type":"turn_end","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We need to decide if proposition is demonstrated. Need to examine evidence. Probably need to verify that evidence supports misrepresentation and reliance. From prompt, likely vote \"demonstrated\". Provide concise rationale ≤3 sentences. Use mcp tool submit_council_vote via tool name \"aar_submit_council_vote\". Provide args JSON string.\n\nThus call mcp with appropriate.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cf8241965c6d4fd6a3","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_submit_council_vote","args":"{\"vote\":\"demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\"The record shows Samantha gave a specific deadline assurance while falsely claiming she had read the required essay, and Peter relied on that assurance to keep an expensive rush print slot, satisfying the misrepresentation and reasonable reliance elements on a preponderance basis.\"}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openai/gpt-oss-120b","usage":{"input":12080,"output":165,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12245,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782753263134,"responseId":"gen-1782753263-1I0T4T9xXFnCFYGGrcwW"},"toolResults":[{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_cf8241965c6d4fd6a3","toolName":"mcp","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ok: true\nmember_id: C2\ncase_id: arb-ex01-20260629165458\nphase: deliberation\nopportunity_id: deliberation:1:C2\nremaining_ms: 865141\nattempts_remaining: 3\njson: {\"case_id\":\"arb-ex01-20260629165458\",\"member_id\":\"C2\",\"ok\":true,\"result\":{\"text\":\"Council vote accepted.\"},\"turn\":{\"attempts_max\":3,\"attempts_remaining\":3,\"completed\":true,\"deadline\":\"2026-06-29T17:28:57.827523446Z\",\"deliberation_round\":1,\"member_id\":\"C2\",\"opportunity_id\":\"deliberation:1:C2\",\"phase\":\"deliberation\",\"remaining_ms\":865141,\"role_id\":\"council\",\"turn_numbe